title: Zoomigurumi 3: 15 Cute Amigurumi Patterns by 12 Great Designers
description:
At some point you think it really cannot get any cuter - but it can! In this new book you will find Henry the hippo, Flora the fawn, Wilbur the penguin, Nanook the husky, Puddles the duckling, Boba the giant panda, Clementine the cow, Hedley the hedgehog, Jean the fox, Cuddles the lamb, Orion the turtle, Katy and Kelvin kangaroo, Rusty the red panda, Eugenio the bird and Rudy the Reindeer. 

Learn to crochet these 15 new animals created by 12 talented designers. Projects ranging from beginner to advanced crocheter. Find complete instructions for all basic stitches needed and lots of pictures of each character from all sides.
